Project Details
View
Stair Remodelling
This residential project focused on the professional installation of interior doors and a custom staircase within a private home. The scope required precise measurements, careful planning, and clean execution to ensure seamless integration with the existing interior.

Our team managed the project from preparation to final installation, paying close attention to alignment, finishing, and overall functionality. The result is a refined and durable installation that enhances both the flow and character of the living space.
